#

Cranberry Citrus Spritzer

5 min
$3.5
90 kcal
Difficulty: 5%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

DrinkRefreshingEasy

Description

A refreshing and tangy drink that combines the boldness of cranberry with zesty citrus flavors, perfect for any occasion.

Ingredients

  • cranberry juice: 1 cup
  • sparkling water: 1 cup
  • fresh lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • fresh orange slices: 2 slices
  • fresh mint leaves: 5 leaves
